cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MED, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper proposes a computer-aided diagnosis system for lung diseases using transfer learning, which involves image analysis and classification. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses transfer learning, a popular machine learning technique, to develop the proposed system. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The proposed system involves the use of machine learning and computer vision techniques to aid in the diagnosis of lung diseases. 
4. cs.MED (Medical Imaging) - The paper focuses on the use of bronchoscopy inspection for lung disease diagnosis and proposes a computer-aided diagnosis system for the same. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper proposes a system that can provide a second opinion on diagnosis, which involves retrieving relevant information from medical records and images.
